  "detailed_description": "<br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Fly through danger filled procedurally generated tunnels, avoiding thousands of enemies, on this throwback to the golden age of arcade games. </li></ul><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/562360/extras/ee90ebd635f6289dd76d9364f9dd8410.poster.avif?t=1762262867\" width=590 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/562360/extras/ee90ebd635f6289dd76d9364f9dd8410.webm?t=1762262867\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/562360/extras/ee90ebd635f6289dd76d9364f9dd8410.mp4?t=1762262867\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Perfect to play when you are in a queue for another game or when you want to get your name on the top of a leaderboards. This is a small, re-playable game, the objectives included are to beat your best score, to get on the leaderboards and get achievements.<br></li><li>Inspired by timeless classics like River Raid, 1942, Space Invaders, Truxton, and Galaga, it offers a unstopable action with thousands of bullets and enemies at each run!</li></ul><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/562360/extras/826cd7d3da2496180fb8730ad429bf91.poster.avif?t=1762262867\" width=588 height=248 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/562360/extras/826cd7d3da2496180fb8730ad429bf91.webm?t=1762262867\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/562360/extras/826cd7d3da2496180fb8730ad429bf91.mp4?t=1762262867\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Survive as long as possible avoiding walls and enemies, on a increasingly difficult game. <br></li><li>Get biggers scores by not missing enemies, for every 10 kill your multiplier increases, if 1 enemy pass, the multiplies return to 0.<br></li><li>The difficulty is constantly rising, so destroy the enemies early to get a bigger score.</li></ul><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/562360/extras/cf293b98cd26b37f8af6fd03cb8053eb.poster.avif?t=1762262867\" width=590 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/562360/extras/cf293b98cd26b37f8af6fd03cb8053eb.webm?t=1762262867\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/562360/extras/cf293b98cd26b37f8af6fd03cb8053eb.mp4?t=1762262867\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
  "about_the_game": "<br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Fly through danger filled procedurally generated tunnels, avoiding thousands of enemies, on this throwback to the golden age of arcade games. </li></ul><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/562360/extras/ee90ebd635f6289dd76d9364f9dd8410.poster.avif?t=1762262867\" width=590 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/562360/extras/ee90ebd635f6289dd76d9364f9dd8410.webm?t=1762262867\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/562360/extras/ee90ebd635f6289dd76d9364f9dd8410.mp4?t=1762262867\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Perfect to play when you are in a queue for another game or when you want to get your name on the top of a leaderboards. This is a small, re-playable game, the objectives included are to beat your best score, to get on the leaderboards and get achievements.<br></li><li>Inspired by timeless classics like River Raid, 1942, Space Invaders, Truxton, and Galaga, it offers a unstopable action with thousands of bullets and enemies at each run!</li></ul><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/562360/extras/826cd7d3da2496180fb8730ad429bf91.poster.avif?t=1762262867\" width=588 height=248 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/562360/extras/826cd7d3da2496180fb8730ad429bf91.webm?t=1762262867\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/562360/extras/826cd7d3da2496180fb8730ad429bf91.mp4?t=1762262867\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Survive as long as possible avoiding walls and enemies, on a increasingly difficult game. <br></li><li>Get biggers scores by not missing enemies, for every 10 kill your multiplier increases, if 1 enemy pass, the multiplies return to 0.<br></li><li>The difficulty is constantly rising, so destroy the enemies early to get a bigger score.</li></ul><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/562360/extras/cf293b98cd26b37f8af6fd03cb8053eb.poster.avif?t=1762262867\" width=590 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/562360/extras/cf293b98cd26b37f8af6fd03cb8053eb.webm?t=1762262867\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/562360/extras/cf293b98cd26b37f8af6fd03cb8053eb.mp4?t=1762262867\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
